window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When a running battle brings the Fafnir home to Earth, it ends with the death of a trusted friend—and a new focus on what comes next for Van and his crew.</b></p> <p>The Guild is rotten. It must be changed. It must be healed. But to do that, Van will have to marshal resources on a scale he's never considered, and that means calling in favors from friends.</p> <p>With the Schegith fleet in training, and the Conoku itching to get back into the fight, Van has a clear plan for what he has to do—which is the one thing he doesn't want to do.</p> <p>The time for war is here. The time for change is now.</p> <p>A new leader is needed, and Van will discover if he can take control of Yotov's criminal empire—and save the victims across known space.</p>"; 
